 Hardware \\u0026 Telemetry Engineer\\\"}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[10px] text-foreground-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Alex maintains the Web Gamepad API vendor ID mapping database. He benchmarks input lag and stick drift tolerances across over 50+ gamepad models annually. He is passionate about console preservation and hardware firmware modifications.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-1.5 border-t border-border/60 pt-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",\\\"QA Lead Certified\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"block text-[8px] text-foreground-muted\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"🏅 \\\",\\\"QA Lead Certified\\\"]}]],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"a\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"mailto:alex.mercer@gamepadtester.live\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"block text-[9px] text-accent hover:underline mt-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"✉️ \\\",\\\"alex.mercer@gamepadtester.live\\\"]}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-surface border border-border rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs font-bold font-display text-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Recommended\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"border-b border-border/60 pb-3 last:border-b-0 last:pb-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[9px] text-foreground-muted block mb-1\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Hardware Mods\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L6\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/blog/hall-effect-joystick-swaps\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs font-bold font-display text-foreground hover:text-primary leading-tight transition block\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Hall Effect Joystick Upgrade: End Stick Drift Forever\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"border-b border-border/60 pb-3 last:bor